{"tid":104563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【發老脾外交】特朗普冚澳洲總理電話 難民問題講到火滾","createTime":"2017-02-02T07:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T15:39:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc9373d1a606b94fbfa2ed77b0fb86a1c607453","tid":104563,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170202/large/1486013132_b416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170202%2Flarge%2F1486013132_b416.jpg&h=b1c13eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有報道指，特朗普首次以美國總統身份與澳洲總理特恩布爾（Malcolm Turnbull）通電話，兩人討論起難民問題時不歡而散，特朗普更發火「冚電話」。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓郵報》指，兩人周末原訂通話1小時，但僅交談了25分鐘便完結。他們的話題是關於奧巴馬政府與澳洲達成的協議，美國同意接收大部份被澳洲拒絕的穆斯林難民。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，特朗普當時怒斥這是「史上最差的協議」，指控特恩布爾趁機向美國輸入「下一位波士頓炸彈人」。2013年波士頓馬拉松爆炸案，兩名主謀是吉爾吉斯出生。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又指今次是他與各國領導人對話中最差的一次，隨即掛斷電話。<br />\n<br />\n在報道發佈後數小時，特朗普在Twitter上狠批協議：「你相信嗎？奧巴馬政府同意由澳洲接收數以千計非法移民，為什麼？我會研究這個蠢協議的！」特恩布爾拒絕回應有否遭特朗普「冚電話」，只形容這次對話「坦誠、非公開的」。<br />\n<br />\n白宮對有關協議卻立場反覆，發放的資訊引起混亂。白宮周四傳給澳洲廣播公司的一份聲明指：「總統目前仍在考慮是否推進這項協議。」但其後國務院發聲明稱，美國與澳洲擁有密切關係，美國會履行協議。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56251170&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56251170%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170202&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWvxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=4b393ee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56251170%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170202&h=cffadb12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56251170&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170202</a>"},{"pid":"aeee8826fe5d7942495e14cbcdc0ca199fd37de5","tid":104563,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"Trump: You are fired<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce08cc233468e192e07c317fed3ec8195f72dd5","tid":104563,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細路仔脾氣"},{"pid":"24276abf478473157d43b661d552df7d0ff5fc0e","tid":104563,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"當自己傾緊生意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb6848b6debfbfefe29af3679c6e7f104f2aeb6","tid":104563,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"今次撐癲佬<br />\n奧巴馬幫人地國家收難民係咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62e3662d1d978fd9dc4579eca6f0558bd0bc80c","tid":104563,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"咁奧巴馬都幾賣國<br />\n澳洲都唔撚要既，就要美國人食左佢？"},{"pid":"c6ad508b35629c1ce60bee2d6e3c107f3fc9af4a","tid":104563,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁奧巴馬都幾賣國<br />\n澳洲都唔撚要既，就要美國人食左佢？</blockquote><br />\n世界警察呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a971cfcf62faf204d7b28db887e444c8e36b5b","tid":104563,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"阿侵雖然好撚癲但又好鬼真"},{"pid":"ded44c5cdd41797e7999174f49c0ca57c6ded51d","tid":104563,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁奧巴馬都幾賣國<br />\n澳洲都唔撚要既，就要美國人食左佢？</blockquote><br />\n世界警察呀<img src=\"/assets